## Complete Flow After Fix
```
PO Number
    ↓
LIPS (VGBEL = PO)
    ↓
Delivery Numbers (gt_lips_del)
    ↓
LIKP (FOR ALL ENTRIES) → WADAT → gv_planned_gi ✅
    ↓
VBFA (vbeln = delivery, vbtyp_v = 'C') → Sales Order → sale_ord ✅
    ↓
Dropdown populated ✅
    ↓
On dropdown change → Update WADAT + Sales Order ✅

